data.description: This mountain retreat in the city is the best of both worlds! Nestled at the end of a cul-de-sac on over 1 acre, privacy and seclusion are the best ways to describe this home. The surrounding trees provide shade with just enough room to capture spectacular city and mountain views. Main level has primary and 2nd bedroom. Bathroom has been recently remodeled in a rustic/modern design. Vaulted ceilings highlight the kitchen, dining and living areas anchored by a wood burning stove for the upcoming temperature change. The walkout basement has a large family/rec area with a projection screen ready for movie night! The L-shaped layout provides room for a flex space, you decide! Bedroom 3 makes for a perfect, private guest room with full bath nearby (recently remodeled with modern design!). Laundry and utilities are in the basement. Take a walk out back to unwind in the Bullfrog Hot Tub that stays with this home. You won't see any neighbors behind you as the lot goes past where the eye can see! Detached one car garage and a turn out big enough to fit a camper make parking a breeze. Make this one yours today! Quick close possible!
